11594#define ETH_MACCR_IFG ((uint32_t)0x000E0000) /* Inter-frame gap */

11596 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_88Bit ((uint32_t)0x00020000) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 88Bit */
11597 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_80Bit ((uint32_t)0x00040000) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 80Bit */
11598 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_72Bit ((uint32_t)0x00060000) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 72Bit */
11599 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_64Bit ((uint32_t)0x00080000) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 64Bit */
11600 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_56Bit ((uint32_t)0x000A0000) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 56Bit */
11601 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_48Bit ((uint32_t)0x000C0000) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 48Bit */
11602 #define ETH_MACCR_IFG_40Bit ((uint32_t)0x000E0000) /* Minimum IFG between frames during transmission is 40Bit */
11603#define ETH_MACCR_CSD ((uint32_t)0x00010000) /* Carrier sense disable (during transmission) */
11604#define ETH_MACCR_FES ((uint32_t)0x00004000) /* Fast ethernet speed */
11605#define ETH_MACCR_ROD ((uint32_t)0x00002000) /* Receive own disable */
11606#define ETH_MACCR_LM ((uint32_t)0x00001000) /* loopback mode */
11607#define ETH_MACCR_DM ((uint32_t)0x00000800) /* Duplex mode */
11608#define ETH_MACCR_IPCO ((uint32_t)0x00000400) /* IP Checksum offload */
11609#define ETH_MACCR_RD ((uint32_t)0x00000200) /* Retry disable */
11610#define ETH_MACCR_APCS ((uint32_t)0x00000080) /* Automatic Pad/CRC stripping */
11611#define ETH_MACCR_BL ((uint32_t)0x00000060) /* Back-off limit: random integer number (r) of slot time delays before rescheduling
11612 a transmission attempt during retries after a collision: 0 =< r <2^k */
11613 #define ETH_MACCR_BL_10 ((uint32_t)0x00000000) /* k = min (n, 10) */
11614 #define ETH_MACCR_BL_8 ((uint32_t)0x00000020) /* k = min (n, 8) */
11615 #define ETH_MACCR_BL_4 ((uint32_t)0x00000040) /* k = min (n, 4) */
11616 #define ETH_MACCR_BL_1 ((uint32_t)0x00000060) /* k = min (n, 1) */
